[{"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Oberfinanzdirektion N\u00fcrnbergS-2230 - 85 / St 22EStG: 13aEStG: 55 / 5EStR: 19Income tax of farmers and foresters1 Application of \u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c EStG and accounting obligation"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 deviating from the previous legal situation (\u00a7 12 para 4 no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "3 GDL) the profits from the in \u00a7 13a para 3 no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c EStG is compensated by the basic amount if the comparative values \u200b\u200bof these special branches do not exceed a total of DM 4000 and the Stpfl is neither legally obliged to keep accounts nor voluntarily uses the possibility of determining profits by comparing business assets or by comparing operating income with operating expenses (cf. also Section I No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 and 4 of the OFD-Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "from 5 1 1976 S-2230 - 82 / St 22)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "The question has been asked whether in view of this change in the legal situation from Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 in favor of farmers with a comparative value for all special branches of no more than DM 4,000, the statutory accounting obligation, even if it has previously existed because the profit limit was exceeded, is to be re-examined using Section 13a (2) - 5 EStG"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "There is no legal basis for dealing with such matters"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Accordingly, in all cases in which the FA the Stpfl before the start of Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 due to exceeding the profit limit by special notification (Section 127 Paragraph 1 Sentences 2 and 3 EStR) for bookkeeping no later than the Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 has requested a determination of the profit according to average rates from Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 not possible"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "If the taxpayer does not comply with the accounting obligation, the profit must be estimated"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Only if the request for bookkeeping is not given to the Stpfl before the start of Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 received, the profit can be determined according to \u00a7 13a Abs 2 - 5 EStG (FMS of 7 1 1976 Az"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": ": 31 - S-2149 - 15/4 - 80928/75)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "2 Transitional regulation due to an increase in the profit limit relevant for the accounting obligation from DM 12,000 to DM 15,000 to the FMS of 12 1 1976 Az"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": ": 31 - S-1160 a - 4/11 - 932 (known"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "with OFD-Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "from 23 2 1976 S-1160 a - 4 / St 22) I point out"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "I ask you to write down the cases in which the 1974 assessment is impeded due to the order in letter b) of the FMS and, if the impediment should still persist when the 1974 income tax assessment is completed, to state the number in the final report"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "3 Consideration of stocks in the case of valuation farmers When estimating the profit of a farmer and forestry man who is obliged to keep accounts but does not keep proper books, unless they are based on reference rates (No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "3 of the OFD-Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "dated 3 1 1975 S-2230 - 75 / St 22), in accordance with Section 4 (1) EStG, the comparison of stocks (in particular inventories) must be taken into account (BFH judgment of 21 8 1952 BStBl III p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "259)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "This applies in particular to the profits from special branches of business, if the estimate is based on the actual income"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "4 Transitional taxation according to section 19 EStR and accounting obligation The average taxation according to Section 13a EStG is to be equated with that according to Section 4 (1) EStG (BFH judgment of 3 6 1965 BStBl"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "III p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "576)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Therefore, in the case of farmers and foresters whose profit from special branches of business is previously under Section 4 (3) EStG or as a surcharge under Section 12 (4) no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "3 GDL has been calculated, and now (from Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75) according to average rates (\u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c EStG) is to be determined, a transitional taxation according to Section 19 EStR (see also Section I No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "6 of the OFD- Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "from 5 1 1976 S-2230 - 82 / St 22)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "If the profit limit applicable to the accounting obligation (\u00a7 161 Paragraph 1 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c AO) is only exceeded by the recording of the transitional profit, I ask you to refrain from asking the Stpfl to keep the bookkeeping in accordance with Section 161, Paragraph 2 of the Tax Code (Section III, Paragraph 2 of the RdF Decree of 5 7 1935 RStBl"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1935 p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "953; see no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c of the OFD-Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "from 19 10 1967 S-2230 - 9 / St 22)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "5 Evaluation of the EW notifications for the economic units of the agricultural and forestry assets The basis for the profit determination according to \u00a7 13a EStG are the new unit values"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "The IT department has sent machine-generated EW messages to the tax offices and branch offices for all agricultural and forestry companies"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "According to No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "5 of the OFD-Vfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "from 3 1 1975 S-2230 - 75 / St 22, the EW notifications had to be checked in certain cases"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Because of the unreasonable amount of work, the question of tax liability cannot be checked by sending tax returns in all cases in which EW notifications are available"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Such a review must be limited to those cases in which tax liability can be expected"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "In the following cases, I consider it necessary to send tax returns to farmers and foresters who have not yet been recorded for tax purposes: a) Comparative value for agricultural use of more than DM 30,000 or b) Comparative values \u200b\u200bfor special branches (Section 13a (3) no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 c EStG) a total of more than 4000 DM or c) comparative value of forestry use more than 7000 DM"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "An income tax declaration must also be sent if operational processes have not been taken into account in determining the profit based on average rates (Section 13a (6) no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "3 EStG, z"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "the sale or removal of land, logging, transport services, etc.)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "If a farmer or forester or his wife who has not yet been registered for tax purposes has income from non-self-employed work, the sending of a tax return - provided there is no other income - depends on whether the profit from agriculture and forestry is more than DM 800 is to be expected (Section 46 (2) no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1 EStG); this is usually not the case if the sum of all comparison values \u200b\u200bdoes not exceed DM 4000"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Is from the income tax declaration 1974 with Annex L for the Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 it is not clearly evident that tax liability arises for Vz 1974 (e.g."}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "because of the profit determination according to the GDL for the Kj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1973/74 or because child allowances are taken into account), the 1974 tax return can be evaluated in the course of the 1975 assessment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "The sending of income tax declarations 1973 with Annex L for the Wj"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "1973/74 to determine the income from agriculture and forestry for the VZ 1974 can therefore be limited to individual cases"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "I would ask you to record in a simple form the number of farmers and foresters who have not yet been recorded for tax purposes and to whom income tax returns for 1974 were sent based on the evaluation of the EW reports"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "6 Processing of applications for determination of the partial value according to \u00a7 55 Paragraph 5 EStG The statutory exclusion period of \u00a7 55 Paragraph 5 EStG expired on December 31, 1975"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "In their applications submitted on time, the taxpayers were initially able to designate the properties for which the application for determination of the higher partial value was made (cf. the FMS dated 11 12 1975 Az"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": ": 31 - S-2188 - 1/21 - 75 911 announced with OFD order of 22 12 1975 S-2188 - 13 / St 22)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "It is not objectionable if farmers and foresters have initially submitted the application to determine the higher partial value for their entire property in order to comply with the deadline"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "I ask you to process the applications continuously"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "If they do not contain evidence of the higher partial value, the Stpfl are to be requested to provide appropriate evidence within a reasonable period"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "When calculating this period and when requesting extensions of the deadline, please do not proceed petty"}, {"meta": {"name": "0025698.xml"}, "text": "Income tax / wage tax / church taxBayernLandwirtschaft bodgw-82"}]